---
title: Crispy Tofu Stir-Fry with Red Bell Pepper and Sugar Snap Peas
description: Dredging tofu in cornstarch and frying adds a delicious crispy exterior, adding a perfect surface for the sticky-sweet sauce along with tender veggies. This dish is fun, fast and easy play on delicious take-out.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-tofu-stir-fry-44859a1c.jpg
